To be honest,

4
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:17,340
let me tell you something.

5
00:00:17,340 --> 00:00:20,180
I have a good friend
who works for the imperial court,

6
00:00:20,180 --> 00:00:22,500
specifically in the construction
of dams.

7
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:26,020
However, when he got the funds allocated
by the imperial court,

8
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:27,020
he found that it was less
than 10 thousand silver taels.

9
00:00:27,020 --> 00:00:27,620
Exactly.

10
00:00:27,620 --> 00:00:28,390
My friend was afraid

11
00:00:28,390 --> 00:00:29,820
that it couldn't be finished on time,

12
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:33,380
so he intended to report this matter
to the imperial court.

13
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:34,930
However, he was prevented

14
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:36,260
by the faction
supporting the Crown Prince.

15
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:38,020
Xie Yuheng is truly despicable.

16
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:42,340
I have already sent someone
to investigate

17
00:00:42,340 --> 00:00:44,420
the imposter who pretended to be me.

18
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:45,870
It was a couple

19
00:00:45,870 --> 00:00:47,860
using the alias of "Banjiu."
[*turtle dove]

20
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:48,620
Yes.

21
00:00:49,300 --> 00:00:50,100
Banjiu?

22
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:51,260
That's right.

23
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:52,980
The rumors about the Banjiu couple
are terrifying.

24
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:55,580
Both humans and ghosts all fear them.

25
00:00:55,580 --> 00:00:56,980
Everyone who fought them dies.

26
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:58,380
No one has survived.

27
00:00:58,380 --> 00:00:59,860
Where can we find this couple?

28
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:02,900
I'll find a way to make an appointment
with the Banjiu couple for you,

29
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:05,340
but you must remember

30
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:07,340
this secret passphrase.

31
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:10,420
Ghosts knock on the door at midnight.

32
00:01:10,780 --> 00:01:12,220
The passers by are in deep sorrow.

33
00:01:13,580 --> 00:01:14,700
Right.

34
00:01:24,820 --> 00:01:27,100
My love, you are so beautiful.

35
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:35,220
You naughty man, always tease me.

36
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:46,420
Don't tell me
they are the terrifying couple

37
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:49,100
that can make both humans
and ghosts tremble.

38
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:55,540
We are a married couple.
You can't call it "teasing".

39
00:01:56,140 --> 00:01:59,020
This is called flirting.

40
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,420
You naughty man.

41
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:05,340
People are watching us.

42
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,340
I feel so shy.

43
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,380
What a bummer.

44
00:02:10,380 --> 00:02:13,220
I'll go get rid of them now.

45
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:16,740
Ghosts knock on the door at midnight.

46
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:21,260
The passers by are in deep sorrow.

47
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:24,780
Oh, you're here to borrow money.

48
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:26,180
