49
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:27,740
How much do you need?

50
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:30,140
Ten thousand taels.

51
00:02:30,540 --> 00:02:31,740
Ten thousand taels?

52
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,900
That's a huge sum.

53
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,620
They must harbor bad intentions.

54
00:02:43,180 --> 00:02:44,020
Darling,

55
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,820
get rid of them.

56
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:38,490
the Banjiu couple have been taken

57
00:03:38,490 --> 00:03:39,980
to the Three Judicial Departments
for trial.

58
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:42,020
There will be results soon.

59
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:45,660
They are really

60
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:47,620
all bark and no bite.

61
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:50,140
You defeated them in no time.

62
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:52,380
Su Ying, you're truly remarkable.

63
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:54,740
Ying.

64
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:01,180
Have you been poisoned?

65
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:14,460
Your Highness.

66
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:17,020
Do you remember
what I just told you?

67
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:18,340
Yes.

68
00:04:18,340 --> 00:04:20,500
