for thirty years.

75
00:04:30,980 --> 00:04:31,940
We're professionals.

76
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:33,700
As soon as she wakes up, I'll...

77
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:35,700
Good.

78
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:43,500
See you, Your Highness.

79
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:53,420
You...

80
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:00,700
Don't move.
I'll help you suck out the poison.

81
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:13,220
♪A thousand sails
fade into the distant past♪

82
